The ideal sports accessory for runners, whether enthusiasts of professionals. They come in 3 sizes so they adapt perfectly to the calf and they support movement. They are comfortable, breathable and have great thermal resistance.

title: Wallet with RFID Protection and Power Bank Sbanket InnovaGoods
item_description:
If you are passionate about the world of gadgets, InnovaGoods offers you the best and most original new items for the home, car, travel, children, technology, entertainment, etc.! Discover a wide range of high-quality products that stand out thanks to their functionality, efficiency and innovative design, such as the Wallet with RFID Protection and Power Bank Sbanket InnovaGoods!

This original card holder with RFID protection and power bank will help to protect your bank and ID cards from electronic theft and will enable you to charge your mobile phone easily. It includes a triple connector USB cable: Micro USB, Lightning and Type C.

A multifunction security card holder and power bank with a modern and elegant design that will get you out of any difficult situation, so that you can feel at ease and be safe wherever you are.

  • Security, anti-electronic theft (RFID): the RFID (Radio Frequency Identification) blocking technology protects the information that is stored on the cards. This wallet-card holder blocks signals and creates a protective barrier around the RFID cards stored inside it, thereby preventing any nearby RFID readers from reading or accessing the information on credit cards, ID cards, etc. Your cards will be kept safe from scanning by unauthorised contact!  
  • 2-in-1, multifunction: our power bank-security card holder will help you to keep your cards well organised and safe, as well as being extremely useful as an external portable battery for charging your smartphone easily anywhere and at any time. 
  • Card holder: this aluminium card holder is robust, elegant and extremely practical. It has 5 compartments with an “open book” design where you can organise and store your bank cards, ID cards, etc. Its pressure safety closure prevents theft or loss due to accidental opening. 
  • Power bank: our charger card holder (Li-ion battery, 2500 mAh 9.25 W) has a USB port and a Micro USB port. It also has 4 LED charging lights that light up together when charging is complete (approx. 2.5 hrs).
  • Triple USB cable: this card holder-power bank includes a 40 cm USB cable with a triple connector end consisting of: Micro USB, Lightning and Type C, which will enable you to charge a large variety of devices.
